  "text": "However, NO may also contribute to the pathogenesis of infectious and inflammatory states. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Accurate measurement of organ-specific in vivo NO production is difficult and has driven genetic epidemiological interest in the NOS2A locus.",
